'''Baby Jesus''' was a member of an Jew shat out in [[Area 51|Bethlehem]], [[Georgia, USA]]. This event was most accurately depicted in the 1995 movie "Species". The most likely candidate for the [[father]] was [[Joe Jonas|Joseph]], a 31 year old [[lazy|unemployed]] [[neckbeard]] with [[my tiny dick|micropenis]]. Upon his denial that the [[Glenn Beck|child]] was his, [[teen mothers|Mary]] forced him to appear on [[Maury]] and take a DNA test to find out once and for all if the black person was his.  

He never cries, save for when people [[fap|masturbate]].  To make Baby Jesus cry is [[Gg|almost as awesome as winning the internet]], but many people love doing it anyway. Christians love to make him cry, and then repent by [[money|buying]] him some [[prostatot]]s. This shows that [[Christian]]s are indeed [[pedo]]s, because it is documented in [[The Bible|Their "Holy Grail"]] that he grew from an infant to an [[adult]].

The [[lulz]] ensues when you and your black person steal the Baby Jesus from peoples' [[Christmas]] decor and strap him to the hood of your car. However, this is becoming difficult with [http://www.engadget.com/2008/12/03/baby-jesus-and-co-get-free-gps-devices-this-holiday-season/ the advent of new technology].
== The Euphemism ==

'Baby Jesus' is also frequently used as a way for poor, white trash [[Christian|fundies]] to tell their kids not to buttrape their neighbors in the trailer park.  Shitting in one's nest is not something baby Jesus would do (contrary to adult Jesus; see: [[Jesus]]).
